nodes.text: This farming moon was one of the three moons in orbit around the planet Kashyyyk.

The moon held some strategic value as a result of its proximity to the planet Kashyyyk. It was covered with green farmlands and had a breathable atmosphere, although it was filled with pollen. This agriworld was inhabited by farmers and was home to a reptavian species.

During the Clone Wars, a battle took place on the farming moon. Clone troopers on the battlefield had trouble breathing because of the high amount of pollen in the moon's atmosphere, which clogged up their helmet filters. This prompted Grand Master Yoda to order his troops to remove their helmets.
